Topic

Named container for similar events

	You usually create topics to hold different type of Events
	You can create different topics to hold filtered and transformed versions of the same kind of event

Durable logs of Events
  - Append only
	- Can only seek by offset, not indexed 

Events are immutable


Well "Durable logs", the messages does not go. However a topic can configured for messages in it to expire
Retention period is configurable
